<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" xmlns:slash="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/" xmlns:sy="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/" xmlns:wfw="http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/"><channel><title>生活黑客</title><link/>https://lifehacker.com/feed/rss<description>把每件事都做得更好。</description><pubDate> Sat, 16 Nov 2024 23:07:44 +0000</pubDate><language> en-us </language><atom:link href="https://lifehacker.com/feed/rss" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"></atom:link><lastbuilddate> 2024 年 11 月 16 日星期六 23:07:44 +0000</lastbuilddate><copyright>版权所有 2024 Ziff Davis, LLC。版权所有。</copyright><ttl> 15</ttl><sy:updateperiod>每小时</sy:updateperiod><sy:updatefrequency>1</sy:updatefrequency><item><title>我最喜欢的浴室清洁产品</title><guid ispermalink="false">01JCRH98NS9XVJ099BGWG3Z68B</guid><pubDate> Sat, 16 Nov 2024 01:30:10 +0000</pubDate><description>这样你就可以让那些永无休止的苦差事变得更容易一些。 </description><media:thumbnail url="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01JCRH98NS9XVJ099BGWG3Z68B/hero-image.png"></media:thumbnail><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>市面上有数量惊人的产品可以帮助您清洁浴室。您不需要花一大笔钱购买最新最好的产品，但有些产品仍然比其他产品更好 - 作为一个以撰写清洁为生的人，您可以想象我已经测试了其中的很多产品。以下是我多年来发现的最好的。</p><h2 id="the-two-best-products-for-cleaning-most-of-the-bathroom">清洁大部分浴室的两种最佳产品</h2><p>首先，不要再担心如何清洁浴缸、水槽、马桶和固定装置。您实际上只需要两种产品，而且它们的效果都非常好。对于瓷器和瓷砖，选择一些柔软的磨砂膏。两年前的夏天，我第一次接触到这个产品，当时我的男朋友突然决定买一艘船。每天晚上靠岸时，我们的任务是擦掉覆盖在表面的咸水，很快就发现混合了少量磨损和大量泡沫的 Soft Scrub 是最有效且危害最小的产品。从那里，我买了一些放在房子周围。我认为它就像是我的东西的温和去角质剂：它会轻微地抛光和重新表面，不会刮伤，并且会起泡以提供良好的清洁效果。对于浴室， <a href="https://zdcs.link/98bD1O?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Roundups&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=try%20a%20formulation%20with%20bleach&amp;short_url=98bD1O&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开">尝试使用含有漂白剂的配方</a>。 </p><div class="mb-4 rounded-md border-2 border-gray-100 py-7 shadow-xl md:py-6"><div class="order-1 mx-auto flex flex-col justify-center md:order-2 md:ml-4 md:w-full md:grow"><div class="block cursor-pointer text-center font-akshar text-2xl font-medium leading-7 text-brand-green duration-200 ease-in-out hover:text-brand-green-700 md:text-left md:text-xl md:leading-6">柔软磨砂洁面液，含漂白剂，白色 24 盎司</div><div class="mt-4 hidden md:flex md:justify-between"><div class="self-end"><div class="mb-0 h-11 md:flex md:flex-col md:justify-center"><div class=" font-sans leading-4 text-black"><div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-1 md:justify-start"><span class="font-bold"><span class="font-medium">亚马逊</span>7.85 美元</span></div><div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-x-1 font-bold md:justify-start"><span class="text-sm line-through">$9.99</span><span class="text-sm text-brand-green">节省 $2.14</span></div></div></div></div><div class="w-44 self-end"> <button class="flex justify-center items-center w-full bg-brand-green text-white text-base font-sans font-medium rounded-md hover:bg-brand-green-700 hover:cursor-pointer md:text-sm h-11">了解更多</button></div></div></div><div class="order-2 mt-5 h-auto w-full md:order-1 md:mt-0 md:hidden"><div class="flex aspect-video items-center justify-center"><img class="m-0 max-h-full max-w-full rounded-md" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/product/065ZMwrLPWiinGWfjUc2f9n/hero-image.fill.size_autoxauto.v1731694021.jpg" alt="柔软磨砂洁面液，含漂白剂，白色 24 盎司" width="auto" height="auto" loading="lazy"></div></div><div class="order-2 ml-2 hidden w-32 shrink-0 items-center md:order-1 md:ml-0 md:flex"><div class="flex aspect-video items-center justify-center"><img class="m-0 max-h-full max-w-full rounded-md" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/product/065ZMwrLPWiinGWfjUc2f9n/hero-image.fill.size_autoxauto.v1731694021.jpg" alt="柔软磨砂洁面液，含漂白剂，白色 24 盎司" width="auto" height="auto" loading="lazy"></div></div><div class="order-3 flex grow flex-wrap md:hidden md:grow-0"><div class="mt-4 w-full"> <button class="flex justify-center items-center w-full bg-brand-green text-white text-base font-sans font-medium rounded-md hover:bg-brand-green-700 hover:cursor-pointer md:text-sm h-11">了解更多</button></div><div class="mx-2 mt-4 w-full"><div class=" font-sans leading-4 text-black"><div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-1 md:justify-start"><span class="font-bold"><span class="font-medium">亚马逊</span>7.85 美元</span></div><div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-x-1 font-bold md:justify-start"><span class="text-sm line-through">$9.99</span><span class="text-sm text-brand-green">节省 $2.14</span></div></div></div></div></div></div><p>对于您的固定装置，例如水龙头甚至马桶冲水器，我推荐与厨房金属<a href="https://lifehacker.com/home/best-kitchen-cleaning-products" target="_blank">相同的东西</a>： <a href="https://zdcs.link/QKDAgn?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Roundups&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=Brasso&amp;short_url=QKDAgn&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开">Brasso</a> 。这种七合一抛光剂价格便宜（不到 5 美元），可以轻松使铜、钢、铬等材料闪闪发光。</p><h2 id="for-those-tougher-spots">对于那些比较困难的地方</h2><p>过去，我建议使用<a href="https://zdcs.link/KK5xV?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Roundups&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=electronic%20scrubbing%20brushes&amp;short_url=KK5xV&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开">电子擦洗刷</a>，这非常有助于减轻擦洗瓷砖、水泥浆和缝隙的负担。不过，自从我开始使用更具研磨性的软磨砂膏以来，我发现这些有点不必要。对于我确实需要额外擦洗的东西，我<em>再次</em>推荐一些我也建议在厨房使用的东西：我值得信赖的<a href="https://zdcs.link/aB1GgJ?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Roundups&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=Mr.%20Clean%20Magic%20Eraser%20Extra%20Foamy&amp;short_url=aB1GgJ&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开">Mr. Clean Magic Eraser Extra Foamy</a> 。你可以花不到 10 美元买到五个，如果它没有坏，就不要修理它。我买一包并在家里到处使用。与传统的三聚氰胺海绵一样，它们可以快速清除粘稠的污渍和磨损，但内部有小泡沫清洁剂，它们还可以产生额外的去污能力。</p><p>也就是说，如果你有一堆微小的缝隙，那么其中一个电子刷可能仍然适合你。当这样的东西存在并且只有 20 美元左右时，真的没有充分的理由让你的肘部过度劳累。 </p><div class="mb-4 rounded-md border-2 border-gray-100 py-7 shadow-xl md:py-6"><div class="order-1 mx-auto flex flex-col justify-center md:order-2 md:ml-4 md:w-full md:grow"><div class="block cursor-pointer text-center font-akshar text-2xl font-medium leading-7 text-brand-green duration-200 ease-in-out hover:text-brand-green-700 md:text-left md:text-xl md:leading-6"> Rubbermaid Reveal 多功能磨砂刷</div><div class="mt-4 hidden md:flex md:justify-between"><div class="self-end"><div class="mb-0 h-11 md:flex md:flex-col md:justify-center"><div class=" font-sans leading-4 text-black"><div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-1 md:justify-start"><span class="font-bold"><span class="font-medium">亚马逊</span>19.98 美元</span><img class="mt-0 h-[15px]" src="/images/amazon-prime.svg" title="亚马逊 Prime" alt="Amazon Prime"></div></div></div></div><div class="w-44 self-end"> <button class="flex justify-center items-center w-full bg-brand-green text-white text-base font-sans font-medium rounded-md hover:bg-brand-green-700 hover:cursor-pointer md:text-sm h-11">了解更多</button></div></div></div><div class="order-2 mt-5 h-auto w-full md:order-1 md:mt-0 md:hidden"><div class="flex aspect-video items-center justify-center"><img class="m-0 max-h-full max-w-full rounded-md" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/product/02vchN9jvzXUshDVyipb3oM/hero-image.fill.size_autoxauto.v1724255544.jpg" alt="Rubbermaid Reveal 多功能磨砂刷" width="auto" height="auto" loading="lazy"></div></div><div class="order-2 ml-2 hidden w-32 shrink-0 items-center md:order-1 md:ml-0 md:flex"><div class="flex aspect-video items-center justify-center"><img class="m-0 max-h-full max-w-full rounded-md" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/product/02vchN9jvzXUshDVyipb3oM/hero-image.fill.size_autoxauto.v1724255544.jpg" alt="Rubbermaid Reveal 多功能磨砂刷" width="auto" height="auto" loading="lazy"></div></div><div class="order-3 flex grow flex-wrap md:hidden md:grow-0"><div class="mt-4 w-full"> <button class="flex justify-center items-center w-full bg-brand-green text-white text-base font-sans font-medium rounded-md hover:bg-brand-green-700 hover:cursor-pointer md:text-sm h-11">了解更多</button></div><div class="mx-2 mt-4 w-full"><div class=" font-sans leading-4 text-black"><div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-1 md:justify-start"><span class="font-bold"><span class="font-medium">亚马逊</span>19.98 美元</span><img class="mt-0 h-[15px]" src="/images/amazon-prime.svg" title="亚马逊 Prime" alt="Amazon Prime"></div></div></div></div></div></div><h2 id="other-bathroom-cleaning-essentials">其他浴室清洁必需品</h2><p>我还在浴缸里放了一个微型橡胶扫帚，当我洗完澡后，用它来清洁玻璃。这大大减少了我一般清洁玻璃的频率和力度，因为它可以防止水分积聚并在水渍和条纹开始之前阻止它们。 <a href="https://zdcs.link/z3brEK?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Roundups&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=Here%20is%20the%20one%20I%20have&amp;short_url=z3brEK&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开">这是我有的</a>，不到 10 美元。 </p><div class="mb-4 rounded-md border-2 border-gray-100 py-7 shadow-xl md:py-6"><div class="order-1 mx-auto flex flex-col justify-center md:order-2 md:ml-4 md:w-full md:grow"><div class="block cursor-pointer text-center font-akshar text-2xl font-medium leading-7 text-brand-green duration-200 ease-in-out hover:text-brand-green-700 md:text-left md:text-xl md:leading-6">多用途不锈钢淋浴刮刀，适用于淋浴玻璃门，带 2 个粘钩，浴室清洁工具家用窗户镜子刮刀，清洁瓷砖墙壁，汽车，10 英寸银色</div><div class="mt-4 hidden md:flex md:justify-between"><div class="self-end"><div class="mb-0 h-11 md:flex md:flex-col md:justify-center"><div class=" font-sans leading-4 text-black"><div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-1 md:justify-start"><span class="font-bold"><span class="font-medium">亚马逊</span>9.49 美元</span><img class="mt-0 h-[15px]" src="/images/amazon-prime.svg" title="亚马逊 Prime" alt="Amazon Prime"></div><div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-x-1 font-bold md:justify-start"> <span class="text-sm line-through">$14.98</span><span class="text-sm text-brand-green">节省 $5.49</span></div></div></div></div><div class="w-44 self-end"> <button class="flex justify-center items-center w-full bg-brand-green text-white text-base font-sans font-medium rounded-md hover:bg-brand-green-700 hover:cursor-pointer md:text-sm h-11">了解更多</button></div></div></div><div class="order-2 mt-5 h-auto w-full md:order-1 md:mt-0 md:hidden"><div class="flex aspect-video items-center justify-center"><img class="m-0 max-h-full max-w-full rounded-md" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/product/01ur8mPez6M82kfQGMX7rJS/hero-image.fill.size_autoxauto.v1731694825.jpg" alt="多用途不锈钢淋浴刮刀，适用于淋浴玻璃门，带 2 个粘钩，浴室清洁工具家用窗户镜子刮刀，清洁瓷砖墙壁，汽车，10 英寸银色" width="auto" height="auto" loading="lazy"></div></div><div class="order-2 ml-2 hidden w-32 shrink-0 items-center md:order-1 md:ml-0 md:flex"><div class="flex aspect-video items-center justify-center"><img class="m-0 max-h-full max-w-full rounded-md" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/product/01ur8mPez6M82kfQGMX7rJS/hero-image.fill.size_autoxauto.v1731694825.jpg" alt="多用途不锈钢淋浴刮刀，适用于淋浴玻璃门，带 2 个粘钩，浴室清洁工具家用窗户镜子刮刀，清洁瓷砖墙壁，汽车，10 英寸银色" width="auto" height="auto" loading="lazy"></div></div><div class="order-3 flex grow flex-wrap md:hidden md:grow-0"><div class="mt-4 w-full"> <button class="flex justify-center items-center w-full bg-brand-green text-white text-base font-sans font-medium rounded-md hover:bg-brand-green-700 hover:cursor-pointer md:text-sm h-11">了解更多</button></div><div class="mx-2 mt-4 w-full"><div class=" font-sans leading-4 text-black"><div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-1 md:justify-start"><span class="font-bold"><span class="font-medium">亚马逊</span>9.49 美元</span><img class="mt-0 h-[15px]" src="/images/amazon-prime.svg" title="亚马逊 Prime" alt="Amazon Prime"></div><div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-x-1 font-bold md:justify-start"> <span class="text-sm line-through">$14.98</span><span class="text-sm text-brand-green">节省 $5.49</span></div></div></div></div></div></div><p>对于排水管清洁，我从不使用液体清洁剂或除垢剂。我从来没有发现它们那么有效，至少与<a href="https://zdcs.link/84RZq?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Roundups&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=drain%20weasel&amp;short_url=84RZq&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开">排水黄鼠狼</a>相比是这样。它很长，有一个旋转手柄，可以轻松地从管道中拉出污垢和头发，因此日常使用意味着您不会遇到一堆木屐的情况。</p><p>最后，这是我还没有但非常想要的东西，所以我提到它是一种将我需要的东西放入宇宙的方法： <a href="https://zdcs.link/XoKBR?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Roundups&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=cordless%20window%20vacuum%20from%20Sharper%20Image&amp;short_url=XoKBR&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开"><u>来自 Sharper Image 的无绳窗户吸尘器</u></a>，你可以将其装满水，粘在上面到玻璃上，让我们为您完成这项工作。喷洒玻璃后，它甚至会除去水，然后将其分类到单独的水箱中，这样干净的水和脏的水就不会混合。它的价格是 68 美元，诚然，如果你只有一面小镜子（我有）和一瓶 Windex（我也有），那就有点不必要了，但它非常酷，而且很重要。</p> ]]>;</content:encoded><link/> https://lifehacker.com/home/best-products-for-cleaning-the-bathroom<dc:creator>林赛·埃勒夫森</dc:creator><category><![CDATA[Cleaning & Organizing]]></category></item><item><title>如何与亚马逊客户服务真人交谈</title><guid ispermalink="false">01J01RKMDJK7CR7EG3JFSWFCTN</guid><pubDate> Sat, 16 Nov 2024 01:00:00 +0000</pubDate><description>这是在亚马逊联系真人的最简单方法。 </description><media:thumbnail url="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01J01RKMDJK7CR7EG3JFSWFCTN/hero-image.png"></media:thumbnail><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>亚马逊是世界上最大的零售商之一，这使得超越常见问题解答、用户论坛和 Reddit 线程来通过电话与人真正交谈变得非常具有挑战性。您可能已经通过尝试在亚马逊的“联系我们”页面上联系某人而知道，没有直接拨打的电话号码。这是设计使然。</p><p>幸运的是，还有其他更快的方法可以找到可以倾听您具体问题的人，随着<a href="https://zdcs.link/9wG36y?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=How-To&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=Black%20Friday%20deals%20roll%20in&amp;short_url=9wG36y&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开">黑色星期五优惠的到来，</a>记住这些可能会有所帮助。</p><h2 id="get-a-super-fast-callback-from-amazon">从亚马逊获得超快速回电</h2><p>亚马逊不喜欢您直接打电话，但这不会阻止我们。最快的方法是<a href="https://zdcs.link/QODr57?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=How-To&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=use%20this%20link&amp;short_url=QODr57&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开">使用此链接</a>输入您的号码，让他们立即给您打电话，但如果这不起作用，请尝试以下步骤让亚马逊快速给您打电话：</p><ul><li><p>访问亚马逊的<a href="https://www.amazon.com/hz/contact-us/foresight/hubgateway?pd_rd_w=qaBoO&amp;content-id=amzn1.sym.202ba7d0-eb08-4fd9-8a7a-568b8f32da37:amzn1.sym.202ba7d0-eb08-4fd9-8a7a-568b8f32da37&amp;pf_rd_p=202ba7d0-eb08-4fd9-8a7a-568b8f32da37&amp;pf_rd_r=BYDQCBYW3VN8654XYQVM&amp;pd_rd_wg=9VEZN&amp;pd_rd_r=c165eb6c-0ce1-4f6e-91bf-dd4edd2ad69a&amp;qid=1718041484&amp;ref=sxts_aspa_qna&amp;c_c=235127249" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开" rel="noopener">联系我们</a>页面</p></li><li><p>选择<strong>其他内容</strong></p></li><li><p>选择<strong>我需要更多帮助</strong></p></li><li><p>在客户服务聊天中说“<strong>请求拨打电话”</strong></p></li><li><p>回答“<strong>是</strong>”</p></li><li><p>选择“<strong>与客户服务助理联系</strong>”</p></li><li><p>说“<strong>请求打电话”</strong></p></li><li><p>选择“<strong>好的，我将输入我的电话号码</strong>”，然后单击文本以继续输入您的号码</p></li></ul><div class="eloquent-imagery-image"><div class="flex justify-center"><img class="border border-gray-100" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01J01RKMDJK7CR7EG3JFSWFCTN/images-3.fill.size_423x750.v1731698759.png" alt="与亚马逊聊天框聊天的屏幕截图。" width="423" height="750" loading="lazy" srcset="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01J01RKMDJK7CR7EG3JFSWFCTN/images-3.fill.size_800x1419.v1731698759.png 800w, https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01J01RKMDJK7CR7EG3JFSWFCTN/images-3.fill.size_1400x2483.v1731698759.png 1400w, https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01J01RKMDJK7CR7EG3JFSWFCTN/images-3.fill.size_2000x3547.v1731698759.png 2000w" sizes="(max-width: 1408px) 100vw, 1408px"></div><div class="mt-2"><span class="mt-2 font-akshar text-sm tracking-wide"></span><span class="text-xs inline-block text-gray-600">图片来源：丹尼尔·奥罗佩萨</span></div></div><p>将打开一个新的亚马逊窗口，其“使用我们的呼叫我服务”。您的号码应该会自动填充，但如果没有，请确保输入正确的号码并点击“立即给我打电话”。我在不到 3 秒的时间内接到电话，并在不到 10 秒的时间内与人交谈。</p><p>正如您从屏幕截图中看到的，在聊天中需要进行几次尝试才能让机器为您提供获得回调的选项，但这并不是一点点坚持无法解决的。请记住，亚马逊每隔一段时间就会稍微调整一下这个过程，您的体验可能会因为许多不同的因素而有所不同，但解决方案可能非常相似。</p> ]]>;</content:encoded><link/> https://lifehacker.com/money/how-to-speak-with-a-real-person-at-amazon-customer-service<dc:creator>丹尼尔·奥罗佩萨</dc:creator><category><![CDATA[Shopping]]></category></item><item><title>我今天最喜欢的亚马逊优惠：亚马逊 Fire Max 11 平板电脑</title><guid ispermalink="false">01HVSFYDAA8EEZB261GBEFPZFB</guid><pubDate> Sat, 16 Nov 2024 00:30:00 +0000</pubDate><description> Fire Max 11 是最大的亚马逊平板电脑，目前在 43% 的折扣后处于有史以来的最低价格。 </description><media:thumbnail url="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HVSFYDAA8EEZB261GBEFPZFB/hero-image.png"></media:thumbnail><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p> Fire 平板电脑<a href="https://zdcs.link/QLn0Lb?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Deals&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=around%20since%202014&amp;short_url=QLn0Lb&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开">自 2014 年问世以来</a>，多年来取得了显着改进，同时仍保持其经济实惠的状态。 <a href="https://zdcs.link/QLn0Lb?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Deals&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=Amazon%20Fire%20Max%2011%20tablet&amp;short_url=QLn0Lb&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开">Amazon Fire Max 11 平板电脑</a>提供 Fire 平板电脑系列中最大的屏幕，现在您只需<strong>159.99 美元</strong>（原价 279.99 美元）即可购买；或者多花一点钱购买<a href="https:/